cs.NI, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.SY

The paper discusses the design challenges and solutions for the Tactile Internet, which involves haptic communications in real-time. This topic falls under the category of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as well as Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of 5G cellular networks, which falls under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Robotics (cs.RO) as well as Systems and Control (cs.SY).
